### Login
POST http://localhost:3000/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "email": "Khasim@gmail.com",
    "pin": "123456"
}

####logout 
POST http://localhost:3000/auth/logout

### Get Watchlist (protected)
# After successful login copy the `token` cookie value and add it to the `Cookie` header below as `token=<value>`
GET http://localhost:3000/watchlist


### Add to Watchlist (protected)
POST http://localhost:3000/watchlist/add
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "symbol": "AAPL",
    "name": "Apple Inc"
}

### Remove from Watchlist (protected)
DELETE http://localhost:3000/watchlist/remove/AAPL


### Get Market Movers (protected)
# Note: This route is protected by verifyToken() and requires the Cookie header
GET http://localhost:3000/stock/movers


### Get Single Stock Quote (protected)
# Note: This route is protected by verifyToken() and requires the Cookie header
# WARNING: Calling this will throw a ReferenceError in the backend (companyName is not defined)
GET http://localhost:3000/stock/RELIANCE.NS


### AI News + Gemini Analysis for a Symbol (protected)
# Note: This route is protected by verifyToken() and requires the Cookie header
GET http://localhost:3000/news/RELIANCE.NS


### Google OAuth Login (placeholder)
# WARNING: This route is unimplemented in authApi.js and will hang without responding
POST http://localhost:3000/auth/google-login
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "tokenId": "<GOOGLE_ID_TOKEN>"
}
